(516, 0, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Most Popular</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/disqus-comment-system/''>Disqus Comment System</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=disqus-comment-system&amp;_wpnonce=491e1d87ac&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Disqus Comment System''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>The Disqus comment system replaces your WordPress comment system with your comments hosted and powered by Disqus.</p>\n<h4>Newest Plugins</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/facebook-iframe-link-fixer/''>Facebook Iframe Link Fixer</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=facebook-iframe-link-fixer&amp;_wpnonce=06a55fd75d&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Facebook Iframe Link Fixer''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Facebook won&#039;t let you link from an iframe page to another part of Facebook (without opening a new window). This plugin gives you that ability.</p>\n<h4>Recently Updated</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/intlwp/''>Internationalize WordPress (IntlWP)</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=intlwp&amp;_wpnonce=c6fd243129&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Internationalize WordPress (IntlWP)''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Internationalize your WordPress multisite. Your users can use their local language as sub-domainname or sub-path in your wordpress multisite.</p>\n', 'no'),
